Last Time Rated/Reviewed: > 7 days
 
The URL submitted for review was rated more than 7 days ago. The default setting for Blue Coat SG clients to download rating changes is once a day. There is no need to show ratings older than this.

Since Blue Coat's desktop client K9 and certain OEM partners update differently, ratings may differ from those of a Blue Coat SG as well as those present on the Site Review Tool.
